questions.scenario:
You are debugging a production issue where a high-throughput Spring Boot service hangs indefinitely. The service uses a `ConcurrentHashMap` to cache nested dependency resolutions. Below is the simplified snippet:

java
@Service
public class DependencyCache {
    private final Map<String, String> cache = new ConcurrentHashMap<>();

    public String resolve(String key) {
        return cache.computeIfAbsent(key, k -> {
            if (k.contains("->")) {
                String subKey = k.split("->")[1];
                return resolve(subKey); // Recursive call
            }
            return "BaseValue:" + k;
        });
    }
}
